entry.title: Mac制作MacOS-U盘启动
entry.content: app源制作U盘启动方式 App Store下载Mac OS 格式化U盘为Mac OS X扩展 (日志式)格式,GUID分区图,名称”Sierra”1$ sudo /Applications/Install\ macOS\ Sierra.app/Contents/Resources/createinstallmedia --volume /Volumes/Sierra --applicationpath /Applications/Install\ macOS\ Sierra.app --nointeraction dmg源制作U盘启动方式 格式化U盘为Mac OS X扩展 (日志式)格式,GUID分区图,名称”Sierra” 双击dmg，会磁盘工具里显示相应磁盘镜像 选分好区的U盘,点击恢复,恢复来源选择刚挂载的镜像

entry.title: Windows中Zabbix_Agent服务相关
entry.content: 添加服务1C:\zabbix\bin\zabbix_agentd.exe -i -c C:\zabbix\conf\zabbix_agentd.win.conf zabbix_agentd.exe [976]: service [Zabbix Agent] installed successfullyzabbix_agentd.exe [976]: event source [Zabbix Agent] installed successfully 启动程序1C:\zabbix\bin\zabbix_agentd.exe -c C:\zabbix\conf\zabbix_agentd.win.conf -s zabbix_agentd.exe [2360]: service [Zabbix Agent] started successfully 报如下错误,重启或注销系统[10480]: ERROR: cannot create service [Zabbix Agent][2224]: ERROR: service [Zabbix Agent] already exists[11212]: ERROR: cannot start service [Zabbix Agent] 删除服务1sc delete "Zabbix Agent" 双引号为英文号
